OL,3,CBestselling author Barbara Taylor
OL,4,CBradford dies aged 91
OL,6,FBestselling novelist Barbara Taylor
OL,7,FBradford has died at the age of 91.
OL,9,FThe author, who wrote A Woman Of
OL,10,FSubstance, died peacefully at her home
OL,11,Fon Sunday 24 November following a
OL,12,Fshort illness and was "surrounded by
OL,13,Floved ones to the very end", a
OL,14,Fspokeswoman said.
OL,16,FShe wrote 40 novels during her career,
OL,17,Fwith her most recent, The Wonder of It
OL,18,FAll, published last year.
