OL,6,FAt the age of 20 she moved to London
OL,7,Fand worked in Fleet Street for Woman's
OL,8,FOwn and the London Evening News.
OL,10,FShe met her husband, American film
OL,11,Fproducer Robert Bradford, in 1961.
OL,12,FThey married in London on Christmas
OL,13,FEve in 1963.
OL,15,FThe following year she moved to New
OL,16,FYork to live with him.
OL,18,FThe couple were married for 55 years
OL,19,Funtil he died from a major stroke in
OL,20,F2019.
