OL,6,FTaylor Bradford had started and
OL,7,Fditched several novels while pursuing
OL,8,Fher journalistic career ` until she
OL,9,Fhit the big time when A Woman Of
OL,10,FSubstance was published in 1979,
OL,11,Fmaking her an overnight success.
OL,13,FThe story followed Emma Harte's
OL,14,Fjourney from life as a servant in
OL,15,Frural Yorkshire to heading a business
OL,16,Fempire, despite numerous personal
OL,17,Ftragedies along the way.
OL,19,FIt became a huge bestseller and was
OL,20,Ffollowed by many other successful
OL,21,Fbooks.
