OL,6,FA TV adaptation of A Woman Of
OL,7,FSubstance followed in 1985, starring
OL,8,FLiam Neeson, with Jenny Seagrove
OL,9,Fplaying Emma Harte. It aired on
OL,10,FChannel 4 and went on to garner two
OL,11,FEmmy nominations.
OL,13,FSeagrove said: "It's 1984 and I am
OL,14,Fabout to meet the world-famous legend
OL,15,Fthat is Barbara Taylor Bradford. I
OL,16,Fhave starred in a mini-series made of
OL,17,Fher bestselling novel A Woman Of
OL,18,FSubstance and it really matters to me
OL,19,Fthat she is pleased. I am a young
OL,20,Factress and very nervous.
