OL,6,F"The door opens and all I can say is
OL,7,Fthat a powerhouse of glamour and
OL,8,Fwarmth heads towards me, grabs me,
OL,9,Fhugs me, and says... 'You are my Emma
OL,10,FHarte'. And that was the start of a
OL,11,Flong friendship with the force of
OL,12,Fnature that I am proud to call my
OL,13,Ffriend ` Barbara Taylor Bradford.
OL,15,F"We saw each other whenever she and
OL,16,Fher beloved Bob were in London. I did
OL,17,FHold The Dream for them as another
