OL,6,F"She was a natural storyteller, deeply
OL,7,Fproud of her Yorkshire roots ` she
OL,8,Fwould regale us of her time working on
OL,9,Fthe Yorkshire Evening Post with fellow
OL,10,Freporter Keith Waterhouse and trainee
OL,11,Fphotographer Peter O'Toole, the dawn
OL,12,Fof the Soho cafe society, and the many
OL,13,Fhappy years shared with the love of
OL,14,Fher life, her husband, Bob.
OL,16,F"For 45 years, she was a huge part of
